{
  "info": {
    "name": "GateBuddy API",
    "description": "Comprehensive API for GateBuddy - The Intelligent Airport Companion Ecosystem.\n\n**API Base URL (Local):** `http://localhost:3001/api/v1` (No trailing slash)\n**API Base URL (Railway):** `https://your-app.up.railway.app/api/v1` (No trailing slash)\n\n**Authentication:** Use `Bearer {{token}}` in the Authorization header for protected endpoints.\n\n## Core Ecosystem Features\n1. **Unified OAuth 2.0**: Integrated Google, Facebook, and GitHub sign-in.\n2. **IATA 791 Standard**: Boarding pass scanning with Julian date validation.\n3. **AI Concierge**: Google Gemini-powered chatbot for terminal assistance.\n4. **Indoor Maps**: GeoJSON support for Gates, Lounges, and Retail.\n5. **FCM Notifications**: Firebase Cloud Messaging for real-time alerts.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 AUTH & PROFILE",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Signup",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john.doe@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"passwordConfirm\": \"SecurePass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/signup",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["users", "signup"]
            }
          }
        },
